  "original_title": "\u0da9\u0dd3\u0dc3\u0dbd\u0dca \u0db1\u0ddc\u0db8\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0dc0\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd1\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dc4 \u0db6\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dae\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dcf\u0db0\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Lack of diesel hampers school vans and buses",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Lalith Chandrasiri, Secretary of the All Ceylon School Children Transport Association said that about 75 percent of the vehicles transporting school children ran today (25).",
        "He also mentioned that some school vans and buses could not run due to problems in getting diesel.",
        "Nearly 48000 school vans and buses ply across the island.",
        "Mr. Chandrasiri also said that steps were taken to provide fuel for these school vans and buses through the Langama depot, but problems arose there.",
        "He said that these problems arose due to the increase in the distance to the depots and the release of a limited amount of fuel from the depots.",
        "He further said that from August onwards, all schools will take steps to run vans and buses."
      ],
